{"tid":190180,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 － （有片）一雞兩吃（上集） 豆乳雞湯","createTime":"2017-04-07T03:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T08:39:30.000Z","uid":30742,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"103637461b21edb3a12d8822e2aa149388cbcc8c","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0599ft2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0599ft2.jpg&h=88c765b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係因為有位巴打話想我做華御結既豆乳湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我果頭又無得賣，咁唯有自己摸摸啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身以為係日式湯，應該係味噌啦<br />\n結果第一次完全失敗，變左味噌湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再問巴打係咩味～佢話豆漿+雞湯，<br />\n我終於有d頭緒<br />\n應該係類似砂鍋雲吞雞個樣咁上下<br />\n我就買左隻雞，成隻起骨去做個湯底，但剩左d肉&hellip;<br />\n又唔想落晒落個湯度，結果做左另一樣野～即係『下集』<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，因為我又屎忽痕唔想買盒裝豆漿，<br />\n就自己浸左少少黃豆去做豆漿，豆味會香好多的！<br />\n雞湯一樣可以買現成既雞湯+急凍雞胸去做！<br />\n當然～自家煲係濃好多既！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但無時間或者新手一樣做到！唔洗擔心～都好味既！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X7icMu0rZcU&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX7icMu0rZcU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c7496380\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X7icMu0rZcU&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n豆乳雞湯  圖文食譜: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/04/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F04%2Fblog-post.html&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=afd602ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/04/blog-post.html</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5852069a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=db95fced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2d2a49db\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"e4a7e659cf453c07dca616fcf9b82dbcbabbcd90","tid":190180,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec669985dbd4da5ec91838f172b08cf67cd190f","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa