me":"2017-04-07T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇焗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n焗豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c656dfe85428ba15d9468668e5f3e53823342b4","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定要磨漿劏雞...簡簡單單試下都好味架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1a232ddc188fd394bdcb01144f985741937274","tid":190180,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"我愛老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abeb6b0c8b24ca8bf7e388b6675ec7cd6143c1d3","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我愛老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都愛你～西瓜小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就黎當造喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45218cf4e890e85c556184cb28cd793fd974b940","tid":190180,"uid":24554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"好似幾正咁 <br />\n應該減肥都食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916c8a9b11d134709726c134ce124450c3a9669e","tid":190180,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"老娘煮野咁叻你老公就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5494f24b621b3402be3e60343ee7074c1629ff","tid":190180,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309eb8d4920cf3cd26c309e0849da8af535006c8","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似幾正咁 <br />\n應該減肥都食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雞湯其實都幾油架～雖然會比d菜吸晒～<br />\n真係想減肥要改用菜頭淆湯～會再清d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1628ea53518c0307a4b6d42b6823cf0e1cc7f121","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老娘煮野咁叻你老公就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜我未嫁～<br />\n我身邊好多人仔都生埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c77d47d343a59f3f55d96a5fd82e8220f75636","tid":190180,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c037dac192e4ae8d71c7a931e8606d15a097df3","tid":190180,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:13:24.000Z","msg